channel.title: InsaniiTY! | ALL SKILLS | ORIGINAL HOME | all NPCS! | ORIGINAL TRAINING AREA!
channel.description:
Notice this is my first ever source release there fore i am a begginer in coding!Also note that this is delta dont flame!!! There is not anti-leech in it either, but if you do leech and use it atleast give me a little credit :)
Helpfull commands! (some added by me) ::droprandom ::dropteaser ::dropdragon ::dropbarrows ::droprune ::dropswords ::dropweps (drops random stuff around you for easy drop parties ::ban ::jail ::xteleto ::xteletome ::xtele ::jake ::donarzone ::staffzone ::checkinv ::checkbank ::mute ::ipban ::ipmute and i think theres some more i just forget
------------ Features
100% WORKING NPCS! PERFECT COMBAT!!! All SKILLS WORKING! All Npc's (CORP BEAST, KBD, DAGGANOTHS GWD BOESSES ETC.) Perfected DRAGON CLAWS! Dragon HAI! ALL PVP ARMOUR Very STABLE! LOADS MORE LOG N AND SEE YOURSELF :]
Lets just do the credits now before i forget them 50% to the owner of EvolutionX for the source 48% to me for fixing alot of bugs adding some new stuff and getting a better client 2% to the owner of chemicalX (anthony) for helping me wit some small bugs
Notice it says chemicalx cuz i set it that way cause i let my friend use it while he was working on his source!! [IMG]http://i758.photobucket.com/albums/xx224/hdmodzz/Homenig.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i758.photobucket.com/albums/xx224/hdmodzz/Corpbeast.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i758.photobucket.com/albums/xx224/hdmodzz/Highlvltrain.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i758.photobucket.com/albums/xx224/hdmodzz/allteles.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i758.photobucket.com/albums/xx224/hdmodzz/general.jpg[/img]
OK Later on ill add more pics and stuff but for now i gotta go and this thing keeps messing up idk why but it is. anyways if your new coder use it and see what you can do :), if you a expeirenced coder please no hate comments and you can use it too :)
Download link: http://uppit.com/th8x4jexp6to/Insaniity.rar (its a package)
